{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><p>李家鼎（鼎爺）前妻施明的喪禮於今日（4月22日）於大圍寶福紀念館設靈，大批藝人前來悼念，除了有受訪的鍾志光與黃夏蕙，還久未露面的資深音樂人聶安達Anders Nelsson、施明妹夫鄧梓峰、龐郭秀雲、麥子雲等人，其中麥子雲再度暴瘦現身，令人非常擔心。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123708068660645888356098.jpeg/1cOKeUdJ1QQbQdwiHVnpj6hPI0_59y-_rc_-uZvP_rk\" alt=\"鄧梓峰（葉志明攝）\"><figcaption>鄧梓峰（葉志明攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123708065342820352945310.jpeg/UiYOqFlyz--uHA_vyC1QpGVyu6pb1_09uwK_Ro0Cv0Y\" alt=\"龐郭秀雲（葉志明攝）\"><figcaption>龐郭秀雲（葉志明攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123708077850759168653402.jpeg/QDZGuqZwsbIa820s7WLWjjOeOrw93u-ahVmOt7NZjrc\" alt=\"龐郭秀雲（葉志明攝）\"><figcaption>龐郭秀雲（葉志明攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123708074725871616836401.jpeg/OVSs-tHqv-nZ_PcehdcOptuuTm4bCwatWmwsgGxsLIA\" alt=\"（葉志明攝）\"><figcaption>（葉志明攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123708072058163200796423.jpeg/3DbVf8qMNXQL1trMMSnvxILMGoW2psoFKGGEjx5hhI8\" alt=\"麥子雲（葉志明攝）\"><figcaption>麥子雲（葉志明攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123708069306568704415607.jpeg/jcsx3KojQNTQeF30AExh0dM9a268cPmOhCazc7Ims3M\" alt=\"麥子雲（葉志明攝）\"><figcaption>麥子雲（葉志明攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123708066198458368263841.jpeg/ToMfVgFj5iobtfVAXdDCxcvFDg-acn7Z_fKeOMvynjg\" alt=\"麥子雲（葉志明攝）\"><figcaption>麥子雲（葉志明攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123678018330562560576148.jpeg/80S5vNb6R-PZqTkhd2fg1D2bU-VIYi9n1Znln-OZ5Z8\" alt=\"聶安達Anders Nelsson前來悼念施明。（葉志明攝）\"><figcaption>聶安達Anders Nelsson前來悼念施明。（葉志明攝）</figcaption></figure></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-22T12:13:11.252473+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":225,"images":8,"source":"HK01 娛樂","fallback":"none"}}